| Area | Before | After |
|---|---|---|
| **Security headers** | None | `helmet()` adds ~11 headers |
| **Rate limiting** | None | 100 req / 15 min per IP |
| **Body parsing** | None | JSON + URL-encoded with 10KB limit |
| **Error handling** | None (stack trace leak) | Global handler, sanitized in production |
| **404 handling** | Express default HTML page | Clean JSON response |
| **CORS** | Implicit | Explicit configuration |
| **Graceful shutdown** | None | SIGTERM/SIGINT with timeout |
| **Port config** | Hardcoded `3000` | `process.env.PORT` with fallback |
| **`x-powered-by`** | Exposed | Disabled |

