// FIX
const PORT = parseInt(process.env.PORT, 10) || 3000;
app.listen(PORT, () => {
  console.log(`Server running on port ${PORT}`);
});
```

---

### 9. No HTTPS Enforcement (OWASP A02: Cryptographic Failures)

There's no TLS termination or HTTP→HTTPS redirect. All data, including user PII, would transit in plaintext.

**Fix — redirect HTTP to HTTPS (or enforce via middleware):**
```js
